rules.name: unused-eip-list
rules.description: List any EIP with no instances attached
rules.rulesYaml:
policies:
  - name: unused-eip-list
    resource: network-addr
    description: 'List any EIP with no instances attached'
    filters:
      - type: value
        key: InstanceId
        value: absent
      - type: value
        key: AssociationIds
        value: absen

rules.name: s3-bucket-version-enabled-list
rules.description: List buckets where versioning is enabled
rules.rulesYaml:
policies:
  - name: s3-bucket-version-enabled-list
    resource: s3
    description: List buckets where versioning is enabled
    filters:
      - 'Versioning.Status': 'Enabled'
